  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 6 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bc1 7 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd ?  \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9 ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bomb attack in the country on the 6th or 7th? What is stated in the letter written by the Inspector General of Police to the Defense Secretary?",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Inspector General of Police Chandana Wickramaratne has informed Defense Secretary General Kamal Gunaratne that tomorrow (6) or the day after tomorrow (7) a bomb attack or sabotage may take place in the North, East or South, with the intervention of a foreign intelligence service.",
        "IGP/PA/CID/OUT/1687/22 through a letter dated 27th June, the Inspector General of Police has notified this to the Defense Secretary.",
        "On June 27th, the Deputy Inspector General of Criminal Investigation Department informed the Director General of Police through a letter COM/PA/DIG/CID/OUT/20/2022.",
        "On the Black Tigers Day, which will be commemorated on July 6 and 7, 2022, bombing or any other subversive action targeting the North, East or South will be carried out by a foreign intelligence agency.",
        "It is known that there are preparations to blame the LTTE organization for the destructive action to be carried out.",
        "It has been informed to me that his personal spy information has been given to Police Sergeant Das Gupta (64975) who is serving in the intelligence section of the Anti-Terrorism and Investigation Division that even now, those serving in foreign companies and nobles in Jaffna territory have been notified not to participate in any event on the upcoming 5th and 6th.",
        "Also, I have been informed that in the coming days, the People's Liberation Front and the Left and Opposition parties are planning to attack the politicians including members of the Regional Council and the Members of Parliament and launch attacks on them and their homes to put pressure on the government and make the government uncomfortable. The Inspector General of Police has informed the Defense Secretary."
      ],
